tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE neural_network_experiments (
  experiment_id INT NOT NULL,
  experiment_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  experiment_description TEXT,
  experiment_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  accuracy FLOAT,
  loss FLOAT,
  PRIMARY KEY (experiment_id)
);

CREATE TABLE results (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_id INT,
    result_value FLOAT,
    result_date TIMESTAMP,
    result_description TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (experiment_id) REFERENCES experiments(experiment_id)
);

CREATE TABLE experiment_results (
  result_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  experiment_id INT,
  result_value FLOAT,
  result_description TEXT,
  result_date TIMESTAMP,
  FOREIGN KEY (experiment_id) REFERENCES neural_network_experiments(experiment_id)
);

CREATE TABLE experiment_participants (
  participant_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  experiment_id INT,
  participant_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  participant_role VARCHAR(50),
  participation_date TIMESTAMP,
  FOREIGN KEY (experiment_id) REFERENCES neural_network_experiments(experiment_id)
);

CREATE TABLE experiments (
    experiment_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_name TEXT,
    experiment_description TEXT,
    start_date TIMESTAMP,
    end_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE results (
    result_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_id UUID,
    result_data JSONB,
    result_date TIMESTAMP,
    CONSTRAINT fk_experiment_id FOREIGN KEY (experiment_id) REFERENCES experiments(experiment_id)
);

CREATE TABLE model_results (
    model_result_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id UUID,
    result_id UUID,
    CONSTRAINT fk_model_id FOREIGN KEY (model_id) REFERENCES models(model_id),
    CONSTRAINT fk_result_id FOREIGN KEY (result_id) REFERENCES results(result_id)
);

CREATE TABLE trainings (
  training_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  experiment_id UUID REFERENCES experiments(experiment_id),
  model_id UUID REFERENCES models(model_id),
  dataset_id UUID REFERENCES datasets(dataset_id),
  start_time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  end_time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE results (
  result_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  experiment_id UUID REFERENCES experiments(experiment_id),
  model_id UUID REFERENCES models(model_id),
  training_id UUID REFERENCES trainings(training_id),
  result_data JSONB
);
